{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762171622729","path":null,"data":{"id":4414,"title":"CTFLife:2025醫療保障計劃保費調整、產品停售及相關事宜","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1756267648841,"tags":["周大福人壽"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">致合作夥伴:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CTFLife就以下事宜作調整安排。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>一、2025醫療保障計劃保費調整</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CTFLife現定於<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">2025年11月23日</span></strong></span>起，將<strong>部分醫療保障計劃(包括現時在售及已停售)之新生意及續保保費</strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>作出調整</strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">，而</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">所有保障範圍及賠償金額</span><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">將維持不變</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 現時在售之醫療保障計劃之保費調整幅度:</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-08-27/mceclip5_c6c32ca574ee4a38908db24c15e1a411.png\" width=\"400\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-08-27/mceclip6_8deba27a97824ce581e4f4fbbe3b63fa.png\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> </span><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">以上保費調整幅度並未包含因年齡增加而作出之保費調整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #4ac599;\"> </span></strong></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><strong style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #4ac599;\">續保保費</span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">將於</span><strong style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">2025年11月23日</span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">或以後之</span><strong style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">首個保單<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">週年日</span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">起調整，客戶最早由</span><strong style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">保單週年日30日前</span></strong><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">起開始收到通知或得知已調整保費。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>二、停售「樂康保」醫療保障計劃之有關安排</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style=\"color: #4ca7ab;\">「樂康保」醫療保障計劃</span></strong>(計劃編號:VFPMNBH/VFPMNBU/VFPMNBHR/VFPMNBUR)將於<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">2025年11月23日</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">起停售</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>下架安排</strong>:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-08-27/mceclip0_dc3a74ed3dc94e439329fe18835fc701.png\" width=\"400\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 請注意:如有關申請(包括所有待處理申請)未能於上述日期或之前遞交及批核，<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">該申請將不獲受理</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>三、彈性理賠安排</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">即日起</span></strong></span>，指定醫療計劃只需符合指定條件將<strong>試行彈性的處理方式</strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">調整餘額索償報銷的賠償項目順序</span></strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">:</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-08-27/mceclip1_51a7a69a1d2f4b78a82e9991440f5e6c.png\" width=\"400\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>四、醫療增值服務推廣</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CTFLife的<strong><span style=\"color: #4ca7ab;\">增值服務</span></strong>包括<strong>基本和高端服務</strong>。</span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: justify; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">基本服務適用於<span style=\"color: #4ca7ab;\">自願醫保「悅康保」、「摯康保」、「樂康保」、「卓康保」、「摯康健」醫療保障計劃及其他大眾醫療產品</span></span></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: justify; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">高端服務適用於<span style=\"color: #4ca7ab;\">高端醫療產品客戶包括「世逸」及「逸康保」</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>增值服務三大支柱:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-08-27/mceclip2_073261b18f8d4d889c1f04b2f9af55d1.png\" width=\"400\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"background-color: #ffffff; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">詳情請參閱附件。</span></span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"PM-2025038A _TC&EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-08-27/PM-2025038A _TC&EN_f35ff62cd64e45a3b68f71274d692161.pdf","uploadTime":1756262438971,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"2025醫療保障計劃保費調整產品資料冊.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-08-27/2025醫療保障計劃保費調整產品資料冊_a5c42a8d0f894229b960a3ac7f12b251.pdf","uploadTime":1756262443115,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"FTLIFE","companyName":"周大福人壽","productCodes":["FTLIFE:BCMIP","FTLIFE:MCIP","FTLIFE:MCIPR","FTLIFE:MCMIPS","FTLIFE:TCMIP","FTLIFE:WCMIP"],"productNames":["樂康保醫療保障計劃","世逸特級醫療保障計劃","世逸特級醫療保障計劃(附加計劃)","摯康健醫療保障計劃 - 特級","摯康保醫療保障計劃","卓康保醫療保障計劃"],"companyCodes":["FTLIFE"],"companyNames":["周大福人壽"],"startEffectiveDate":1763862747344,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}